{"tid":2426902,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Cube「邀穗珍霸凌受害者見面」信件曝光！　網傻眼：理直氣壯？","createTime":"2021-02-28T11:46:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T18:56:59.000Z","uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7ee8df80fc5bb7dcbed551d117a913ebf34d1798","tid":2426902,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T11:46:40.000Z","msg":"南韓女團(G)I-DLE成員穗珍遭指控校園霸凌，經紀公司CUBE娛樂第一時間表示「的確有吵架，但不是霸凌」，與被害者A方面僵持至今，韓網上的論戰也相當激烈。近日，有網友上傳了CUBE娛樂寄送的相關信件，內容引起熱烈討論，不少人傻眼直呼「還真是理直氣壯」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5476/d5476816.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5476%2Fd5476816.jpg&h=c64c9082&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲穗珍霸凌風波延燒多日。（圖／翻攝(G)I-DLE IG）<br />\n<br />\n有網友在推特上曬出了CUBE娛樂公關組寄來的霸凌事件相關信件，標題為「[Cube Entertainment]穗珍事件立場傳達」，內容寫道：「您好，這裡是Cube娛樂，由於穗珍提出請求，想與您見面進行真誠的對話，所以聯繫了您。期望能得到您的回覆，感謝。」敘述方式讓不少網友都相當憤怒，認為公司一點誠意都沒有。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5476/d5476817.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5476%2Fd5476817.jpg&h=0ae6901c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲CUBE娛樂公關組寄出的信。（圖／翻攝推特）<br />\n<br />\n南韓網友紛紛批評CUBE娛樂「立場傳達？？？」、「有夠沒禮貌」、「應該是拜託的立場不是嗎？看來不著急吧，誰看到這個會想見你」、「AI（人工智慧）都寫得比這好」、「上次聲明文也是這樣，公司沒有會寫信的人？」、「再怎麼搞不清楚狀況也要有個分寸吧」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5476/5476814.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5476%2F5476814.jpg&h=70db8aed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲南韓網友反應。（圖／翻攝더쿠，翻譯自《ETtoday星光雲》勿隨意擷取）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據悉，Cube娛樂曾與被害者A的姐姐以及律師見面，但穗珍並未到場，Cube方面希望能釐清事實，但A方面想要的是穗珍的道歉，會面最後沒有得出結論。而被害者A的姐姐則透露原先擔心再多說會帶給其他成員傷害，考慮到公司的立場，所以不想再爆出更多內幕，但後來認為無法再沉默下去，因此宣布會在3月1日整理所有的被害者意見上傳。"},{"pid":"0f9923660b250b100b20768eed1d9ecadb12dd30","tid":2426902,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T12:03:52.000Z","msg":"你無得撈㗎喎 你驚嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba2752b993b4b760f1b538e28c16fd033d3cdfd","tid":2426902,"uid":274500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T14:50:46.000Z","msg":"3月1 idle要完蛋了？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2c4afa44d4f5473a47e5d4578fee1c17a81a89f","tid":2426902,"uid":152432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:13:25.000Z","msg":"Gidle 要收皮了<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07c0cb0f8dd687397943373232efbbf80f9ee402","tid":2426902,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T05:31:06.000Z","msg":"傻眼貓咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f470b4810a77e6584509d9841c109fab8ba1897","tid":2426902,"uid":109923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T05:32:12.000Z","msg":"clc同idle一齊收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e07eb6ec2647df4803b2bb2174c6495f3e99830","tid":2426902,"uid":145771,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T13:24:10.000Z","msg":"Gidle正式收皮，cube重新捧返clc，之後clc做咗一線女團，elkie就返大陸無人識"},{"pid":"3c747151fdf989c48d1750305b9c905e8167f36c","tid":2426902,"uid":1086,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1e07eb6ec2647df4803b2bb2174c6495f3e99830","tid":2426902,"uid":145771,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T13:24:10.000Z","msg":"Gidle正式收皮，cube重新捧返clc，之後clc做咗一線女團，elkie就返大陸無人識"},"citedBy"